  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/1408d4a806814b7aa3338854437cbc1d.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/1408d4a806814b7aa3338854437cbc1d.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone can climb a mountain just by playing the right cards in Yamafuda! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you reach one of the ten stations along the mountain, you get to choose a new card and to create gear that will help you get through the next stretch of the trail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But not all trails are made equal! When the weather changes, even a short climb can become challenging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use an ever-changing deck to climb through the ever-changing scenery in this deck-building roguelike!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/ee966ffec2a03584322e5b62c53eb1ae.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/ee966ffec2a03584322e5b62c53eb1ae.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/ee966ffec2a03584322e5b62c53eb1ae.mp4?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 types of cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 types of gear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 10 mountains to climb</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/e2636b99388a10b5d3d6f67dedf2f8b3.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/e2636b99388a10b5d3d6f67dedf2f8b3.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl saw a mountain far away in the distance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I bet the view from up there is amazing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She was just mumbling it to herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/9777b6ee70559405d10c561e88125892.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But her friend overheard that. <br>What?! You want to climb it?! Let's do it! <br>The next day, she showed up more than ready for it. <br> <br>Let's do this!<br>Their climbing plan was thrown together in a hurry...  <br> <br>Will they be able to reach the summit? <br> <br>Let's go! The mountain awaits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/df26032b5b319ed5746a9ad5cb6a8152.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/df26032b5b319ed5746a9ad5cb6a8152.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/df26032b5b319ed5746a9ad5cb6a8152.mp4?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can show any part of the game you want!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/1408d4a806814b7aa3338854437cbc1d.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/1408d4a806814b7aa3338854437cbc1d.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone can climb a mountain just by playing the right cards in Yamafuda! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you reach one of the ten stations along the mountain, you get to choose a new card and to create gear that will help you get through the next stretch of the trail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But not all trails are made equal! When the weather changes, even a short climb can become challenging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use an ever-changing deck to climb through the ever-changing scenery in this deck-building roguelike!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/ee966ffec2a03584322e5b62c53eb1ae.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/ee966ffec2a03584322e5b62c53eb1ae.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/ee966ffec2a03584322e5b62c53eb1ae.mp4?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 types of cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 types of gear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 10 mountains to climb</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/e2636b99388a10b5d3d6f67dedf2f8b3.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/e2636b99388a10b5d3d6f67dedf2f8b3.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl saw a mountain far away in the distance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I bet the view from up there is amazing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She was just mumbling it to herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/9777b6ee70559405d10c561e88125892.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But her friend overheard that. <br>What?! You want to climb it?! Let's do it! <br>The next day, she showed up more than ready for it. <br> <br>Let's do this!<br>Their climbing plan was thrown together in a hurry...  <br> <br>Will they be able to reach the summit? <br> <br>Let's go! The mountain awaits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/df26032b5b319ed5746a9ad5cb6a8152.poster.avif?t=1768028146\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/df26032b5b319ed5746a9ad5cb6a8152.webm?t=1768028146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727520/extras/df26032b5b319ed574